Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.55,0:00:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.85,0:00:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翌晨的陽光就快來臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.02,0:00:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照進這間充滿煙蒂\N雜亂無章的屋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.76,0:00:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why 聖母瑪利亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.97,0:00:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對溫柔感到飢渴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.14,0:00:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.97,0:00:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼孤單的夜晚\N總是如此漫長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.78,0:00:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛仔褲下的膝蓋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.65,0:00:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被破碎的夢想打溼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.99,0:01:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿著襯衫的胸部太過耀眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.96,0:01:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.96,0:01:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我問妳,昨天我看見了\N你們是什麼關係?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.86,0:01:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.53,0:01:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別跟我裝糊塗\N妳跟男生去了咖啡廳對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.80,0:01:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.07,0:01:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,那個啊\N那只是我中學的同班同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.70,0:01:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湊巧在路上遇見而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.60,0:01:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?你們氣氛感覺蠻不錯的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.54,0:01:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.61,0:01:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是八神妳現在怎麼樣了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.88,0:01:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代老師的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.48,0:01:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.58,0:01:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後來就沒聯絡了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.55,0:01:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是已經死心了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.75,0:02:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少胡說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.29,0:02:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說,你們還有在聯絡囉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.56,0:02:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後來的確沒有再見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.63,0:02:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這並不表示結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.56,0:02:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不表示我已經死心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.11,0:02:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不曉得五代老師\N現在過得怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.49,0:02:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#63 馬力全開的八神\N在遺忘的時刻到來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.37,0:02:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.87,0:02:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?家教?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.20,0:02:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,為什麼你要\N兼那麼多打工呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.61,0:02:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光是這裡就很夠了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.54,0:03:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,因為有些原因…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.52,0:03:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那趟旅行花掉我很多錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.16,0:03:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小學的高年級生\N我想應該應付得過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.47,0:03:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣\N我跟幼稚園的媽媽們說說看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.50,0:03:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,園童們應該有哥哥姊姊才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.54,0:03:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.98,0:03:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你唸哪一所大學?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.45,0:03:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近的家長\N連大學都要挑有名的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.35,0:03:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是要當考生的家教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.35,0:03:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是幫忙教他做功課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.22,0:03:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說,你唸哪所大學啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.12,0:03:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了,反正我沒人要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.13,0:03:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這種程度的大學啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.33,0:03:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得應該在這附近…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.98,0:04:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.72,0:04:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應徵家教?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.59,0:04:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代老師?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.56,0:04:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,那麼按照順序來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.63,0:04:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我先,我先\N-來,好高好高喔,好高喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.13,0:04:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.27,0:04:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,好高好高喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.14,0:04:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,還有一次\N來,好高好高喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.48,0:04:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.00,0:05:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師我在叫你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.51,0:05:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神,妳怎麼會來這裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.18,0:05:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去公寓找你\N結果一之瀨太太說你在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.51,0:05:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是大嘴巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.28,0:05:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好高好高喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.88,0:05:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,接下來輪到誰啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.99,0:05:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.42,0:05:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好,排隊排隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.92,0:05:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好高好高喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.36,0:05:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好高喔,好高喔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.03,0:05:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他好像覺得很困擾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.97,0:05:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,打擾你工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.87,0:05:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好高好高喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.87,0:05:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是很想見老師一面,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.55,0:05:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.58,0:05:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.00,0:06:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代老師果然很體貼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.20,0:06:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是意志薄弱而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.00,0:06:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師,你在應徵家教嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.47,0:06:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.94,0:06:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我介紹個優秀學生給你吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.88,0:06:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個對大學聯考有點擔心的\N高二女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.55,0:06:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貼紙內容妳有看清楚嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.78,0:06:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想教的只到中學生為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.65,0:06:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.69,0:06:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是私立三流大學的學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.12,0:06:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法輔導高中生的學習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.63,0:06:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果跟老師一起唸書的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.06,0:06:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灰色的聯考生活\N一定會變得很愉快的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.74,0:06:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的不行嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.88,0:06:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.68,0:06:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.85,0:06:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了,我還得回去工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.68,0:06:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以再去找你嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.55,0:07:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,不要再見面比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.19,0:07:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我忘了\N好好加油考上大學吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.87,0:07:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.37,0:07:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的錢包…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來付吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.35,0:07:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次一定還妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.42,0:07:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說,還能見面囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.03,0:07:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.93,0:07:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.44,0:07:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-請問…\N-什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.31,0:07:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於這個月的房租
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.87,0:07:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能稍微讓我延一下?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.01,0:07:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題,什麼時候都好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.98,0:08:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.58,0:08:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,你一個人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.72,0:08:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你和那個\N叫八神的女孩在一起呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.89,0:08:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,八神來過這裡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.32,0:08:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白天她來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.49,0:08:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴她五代打工的地方\N她就很高興的跑去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.10,0:08:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說她只是剛好到附近\N順便來看看我而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.43,0:08:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不是那麼對我說的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.47,0:08:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一度消失的戀情之火\N如今又死灰復燃了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.01,0:08:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事最恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.31,0:08:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是這樣呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.11,0:08:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那她怎麼突然來找你?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.98,0:08:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…這個…總之…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.62,0:08:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.02,0:08:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她要開始準備大學聯考
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.33,0:08:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以精神上有點不太穩定\N可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.00,0:08:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也有很多事情也不太穩定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.57,0:08:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該做的事,請務必做好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.17,0:09:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.11,0:09:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.47,0:09:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只到中學生為止啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.34,0:09:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我有個弟弟就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.78,0:09:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.91,0:09:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.51,0:09:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,原來還有這招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.36,0:09:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳有弟弟對不對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.63,0:09:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,我有弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.20,0:09:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借我一下好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.73,0:10:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-什麼?\N-不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.80,0:10:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.67,0:10:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.57,0:10:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託啦,弟弟借我啦\N一個就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.24,0:10:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也只有一個弟弟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.98,0:10:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.28,0:10:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.35,0:10:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.35,0:10:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說是看到你貼的\N應徵家教老師的佈告才打來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.89,0:10:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.39,0:10:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,我是五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.16,0:10:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.83,0:10:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.96,0:10:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天晚上七點鐘是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.20,0:10:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,我等你們過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.77,0:10:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.84,0:10:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要當家教嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.31,0:10:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,明天對方說會帶孩子過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.18,0:10:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等拿到打工的薪水\N我會先付房租的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.55,0:10:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事無所謂啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.78,0:10:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你不要累壞了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.45,0:10:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把全部的精力花在打工上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.59,0:10:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一明年畢不了業就傷腦筋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.86,0:11:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.20,0:11:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個媽媽的聲音還真年輕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.00,0:11:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且好像在哪裡聽過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.41,0:11:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就可以了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.34,0:11:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝,妳真是我的好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.64,0:11:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要請我吃草莓可麗餅\N外加奶昔哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.71,0:11:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.92,0:11:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到妳居然那麼不死心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.09,0:11:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以為妳早就忘了五代老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.36,0:11:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那只是個冷卻期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.46,0:11:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了想知道自己真正的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.07,0:11:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果,妳知道了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.87,0:11:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隔了兩個月\N當我又看到老師笑容的瞬間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.15,0:11:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的小小胸部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.15,0:12:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為熾熱的感動\N差一點都快迸開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.89,0:12:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的胸部的確很小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.03,0:12:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要妳管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.60,0:12:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之,那時候我明白了\N我只要這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.31,0:12:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次我一定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.61,0:12:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要貫徹我的真摯之愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.73,0:12:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接著,到了第二天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.28,0:13:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥,教我寫功課好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.02,0:13:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在很忙,等一下好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.19,0:13:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從今天起要五代哥哥教功課的話\N是要付錢的唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.53,0:13:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.26,0:13:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會向賢太郎收錢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.56,0:13:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世上真有這種怪人\N會付錢叫大哥哥教他功課嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.60,0:13:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這孩子真會講話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.57,0:13:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是母親的家教不好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.24,0:13:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.65,0:13:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多快來了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.78,0:13:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對方說七點要來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.89,0:13:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去門口看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.09,0:13:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.19,0:13:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了,對方叫什麼名字?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.33,0:13:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.57,0:13:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然連對方的名字都忘記問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.47,0:13:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真的當得了家教老師嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.45,0:14:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.06,0:14:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.36,0:14:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問五代老師在嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.09,0:14:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八…八神?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.23,0:14:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.23,0:14:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳為什麼會在這裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.23,0:14:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為家教的事情\N我曾經打過電話給你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.14,0:14:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.04,0:14:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你不問對方的名字\N才會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.74,0:14:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這該不會是妳的弟弟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.75,0:14:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你放心,他是我朋友的弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.22,0:14:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,母親的代理人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.92,0:14:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是妳啊,八神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.56,0:14:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.16,0:14:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見,進來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.93,0:14:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.03,0:14:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.23,0:15:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看到這麼髒的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.80,0:15:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這小鬼還真老實啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.57,0:15:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,四谷,你們在嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.74,0:15:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像中了八神的計
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.21,0:15:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.71,0:15:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她該不會每星期都跑來吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.02,0:15:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,我不會讓她這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.42,0:15:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再讓八神進出這棟公寓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.66,0:15:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你唸幾年級?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.86,0:15:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五年級
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.23,0:15:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的鼻子看起來蠻聰明的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.73,0:15:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟,我不會害你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.10,0:15:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還是找個像樣點的家教吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.84,0:15:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這話是什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.34,0:15:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師,你唸哪一所大學?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.51,0:15:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪一所?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.28,0:15:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.72,0:15:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不敢大聲講的大學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.29,0:15:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位,你們也太多話了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.02,0:16:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正遲早會被拆穿\N不如早點告訴他比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.57,0:16:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小徹,你覺得呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.47,0:16:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於學力必須打個問號\N但是人看起來蠻好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.37,0:16:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.31,0:16:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太過於期待家教會有多棒\N可能也不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.68,0:16:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概就是這樣囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.65,0:16:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,我可以決定嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.02,0:16:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.66,0:16:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,這是鐘點費
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.26,0:16:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先付你一個月份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.16,0:16:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下禮拜開始上課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.57,0:16:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.23,0:16:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收下這東西之前\N有件事我要先搞清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.44,0:16:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神,跟我來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.92,0:17:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看起來像是會拿那孩子當幌子\N跑來這裡玩耍的女生嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.42,0:17:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神,冷靜一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.03,0:17:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她能說得這麼毅然決然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.40,0:17:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起來不像在說謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.50,0:17:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你不相信我嗎?老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.64,0:17:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會來這裡玩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.17,0:17:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.77,0:17:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了\N我只是想把事情問清楚而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.51,0:17:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一,二,三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.25,0:17:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當家教還真好賺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.99,0:17:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.26,0:17:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚要開五代的\N打工敲定慶祝會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.69,0:17:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要好好的瘋一瘋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.03,0:17:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶,好耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.79,0:17:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不請客喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.23,0:17:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不請客喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.80,0:17:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是慶祝你找到工作耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.47,0:17:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛那麼見外呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.77,0:17:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼樣工作\N我的日子還是一樣難過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.61,0:17:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真空虛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.68,0:18:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們給我聽著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.68,0:18:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會請客的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.45,0:18:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽懂了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.92,0:18:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對…我絕對不會出錢請客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.79,0:18:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,酒瓶空了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.76,0:18:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚的酒特別好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.96,0:18:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老闆,再開一瓶新酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.13,0:18:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不會請客喔!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.87,0:18:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再開一瓶新酒,再開一瓶新酒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.55,0:18:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.02,0:18:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶,好耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.88,0:18:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,喝個痛快吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.45,0:18:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不請客喔!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.02,0:18:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡,為什麼變成這樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.59,0:18:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,我手邊沒那麼多錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.03,0:19:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個禮拜怎麼不趕快過去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.48,0:19:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安,五代老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.39,0:19:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果付了房租,錢就全沒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.97,0:19:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子雖然有點臭屁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.14,0:19:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,感覺還蠻聰明的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.81,0:19:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會是個輕鬆的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.71,0:19:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正船到橋頭自然直
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.65,0:19:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你找到家教的工作啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.79,0:19:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.89,0:19:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.23,0:19:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊,我有跟媽媽們提過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.96,0:20:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是都沒有什麼好回應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.90,0:20:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,雖然我跟他們說\N你的人很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.64,0:20:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但現在的媽媽們\N都很在乎大學的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.87,0:20:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在這種時代很難得喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.64,0:20:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然光看人品就選擇了五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.11,0:20:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種人要好好珍惜喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.62,0:20:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接著,家教的第一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.90,0:21:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.43,0:21:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.93,0:21:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天要開始家教了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.30,0:21:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,妳看\N我連小學的參考書都買好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.14,0:21:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請好好加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.94,0:21:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.83,0:21:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多快來了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.81,0:21:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.01,0:21:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.61,0:21:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個聲音是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.45,0:21:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.48,0:22:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神,為什麼是妳來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.96,0:22:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭,你怎麼這麼問\N你明明說今天開始要當我的家教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.53,0:22:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說的是當那孩子的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.73,0:22:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小徹是我母親的代理人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.47,0:22:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別跟我打迷糊仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.14,0:22:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時候他沒有說嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.28,0:22:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,母親的代理人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.78,0:22:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,我可以決定嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.21,0:22:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.72,0:22:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說,那個孩子是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.12,0:22:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才是學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.05,0:22:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,妳不是向我保證過了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.76,0:22:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說妳不會再來這裡玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.79,0:22:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是來唸書的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.47,0:22:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什麼誤會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.14,0:22:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.60,0:22:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡,妳居然敢這樣耍我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.41,0:22:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你一定要解除契約的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.78,0:23:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請把上次付的鐘點費還給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.88,0:23:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.92,0:23:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧,五代老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.53,0:23:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.63,0:23:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會給老師添麻煩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.38,0:23:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是中了她的詭計
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.71,0:23:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師,快點快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.43,0:23:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我爸媽都不在家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.76,0:23:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在跟人家興奮什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.00,0:23:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是五代在八神家\N兩個人單獨唸書耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.67,0:23:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.20,0:23:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,『五代快輸了!\N高中女生的甜蜜陷阱!』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.60,0:24:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你要對她…負責喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.62,0:24:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人坐在黎明的護欄上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:34.21,0:24:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今一直在尋找遺落愛的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.79,0:24:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:54.02,0:24:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳…一陣風…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.39,0:25:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目光交會…只有…再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.57,0:25:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:07.67,0:25:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…在雨中…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:11.01,0:25:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忽然…胸口…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:14.45,0:25:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢…濡濕而發光
